\begin_layout Standard
In thermal equilibrium one is not interested in the S-matrix as there are
 no asymptotic states.
 Rather one is interested in the partition function
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
Z=\mathrm{Tr}\mathrm{e}^{-\beta\hat{H}},
\end{equation}

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $\beta=1/T$
\end_inset

