\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset

.
 Furthermore, the trace operation implies periodic boundary conditions:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray}
Z & = & \mathrm{Tr}\mathrm{e}^{-\beta\hat{H}}\nonumber \\
 & = & \sum_{a}\Braket{a|\mathrm{e}^{-\beta\hat{H}}|a}.
\end{eqnarray}

\end_inset

Writing the matrix element in terms of the functional integral,
\end_layout

